parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause fires, short circuits, and loss of vehicle functionality, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Smoke or fumes from the dashboard

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of wiring insulation can cause short circuits, electrical fires, and loss of vehicle functionality, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
Instrument panel malfunctions can cause loss of vehicle functionality, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
The location of the cup holder near the gear shift can cause electrical system failures, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Liquid spills into the gear shift
causing short circuits and loss of vehicle functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Turn signal malfunctions can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Turn signals fail to turn off

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and unexpectedly
and continues to accelerate until it crashes or is stopped.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clouded or failed headlights can reduce nighttime visibility, increasing the risk of accidents.
Transmission failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission fails to engage or disengage gears
causing the vehicle to stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Water Ingress into Transmission Control Module
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the transmission control module can cause transmission failure, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission fails to change gears or operate properly
often after exposure to water or moisture.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or deploy inadvertently, compromising the safety of the occupants.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in a crash
airbags deploy without warning or impact
SRS light appears on the dashboard
